### ===========================================
### Post2 API テスト
### ===========================================
### 使い方: 各リクエストの上の「Send Request」をクリック
### ===========================================

@baseUrl = http://localhost:8081/api

### -------------------------------------------
### ヘルスチェック（疎通確認）
### -------------------------------------------
GET {{baseUrl}}/health
Accept: application/json

### -------------------------------------------
### 一覧取得
### -------------------------------------------
GET {{baseUrl}}/post2s
Accept: application/json

### -------------------------------------------
### 詳細取得
### -------------------------------------------
GET {{baseUrl}}/post2s/1
Accept: application/json

### -------------------------------------------
### 新規作成
### -------------------------------------------
POST {{baseUrl}}/post2s
Content-Type: application/json
Accept: application/json

{
    "user_id": 1,
    "title": "テストタイトル",
    "slug": "test-slug",
    "body": "テスト本文です",
    "status": "active",
    "published_at": "2025-01-01"
}

### -------------------------------------------
### 更新
### -------------------------------------------
PUT {{baseUrl}}/post2s/1
Content-Type: application/json
Accept: application/json

{
    "user_id": 1,
    "title": "テストタイトル（更新後）",
    "slug": "test-slug（更新後）",
    "body": "テスト本文です（更新後）",
    "status": "active（更新後）",
    "published_at": "2025-01-01"
}

### -------------------------------------------
### 削除
### -------------------------------------------
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/post2s/1
Accept: application/json

### -------------------------------------------
### 検索（ユーザーIDで絞り込み）
### -------------------------------------------
GET {{baseUrl}}/post2s?user_id=1
Accept: application/json

### -------------------------------------------
### 検索（ステータスで絞り込み）
### -------------------------------------------
GET {{baseUrl}}/post2s?status=active
Accept: application/json
